race.comment: The well-related SHAKO (2) (half to G2 winner Arcaded) goes well for hoop Martyn who has a win and two placings from just three steers and has been racing very consistently this time in work. Again gets the benefit of her 3kg claim and should be going very close. KING SPIRIT (5) resumes here but the form he showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this nature. Include from the inside marble. DEFIANT SPIRIT (3) best of the rest with Maloney on board. MAKE IT SO (7) has been back to the trials since a disappointing effort here 42 days ago when well beaten. Her recent trial suggests she may be back on song however. Not willing to discount in this small field.
